title: The Quarterly Review of Biology

contents.note: JSTOR (full text also available for subscription or payment)

additional-note: The March 1966 issue is the first for which a renewal was filed.  Issues copyrighted in 1964 or later would also have their copyrights renewed.  However, if pre-1966 issues were published without copyright notices (which we have not found on a casual inspection of JSTOR scans of this journal from 1964) they would not have been copyrighted.
